f:T584,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"TechArticle","headline":"Menguasai React Server Components di Next.js 14","description":"Pelajari cara memanfaatkan React Server Components di Next.js 14 untuk membangun aplikasi web yang lebih cepat dan efisien.","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"/uploads/1780240471315-mzhf5c.png","width":1200,"height":630},"datePublished":"2024-06-15","dateModified":"2026-05-31","author":{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://abyte.id/#person","name":"Abiyyu Abidiffatir Al Majid","url":"https://a2mdev.site","image":"https://abyte.id/images/author-avatar.jpg"},"publisher":{"@type":"Organization","@id":"https://abyte.id/#organization","name":"abyte","url":"https://abyte.id","logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://abyte.id/abyte-logo.png","width":200,"height":60}},"mainEntityOfPage":{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://abyte.id/id/articles/mastering-server-components-nextjs-14"},"url":"https://abyte.id/id/articles/mastering-server-components-nextjs-14","wordCount":531,"articleSection":"Pengembangan Web","keywords":"Next.js, React, Server Components, Performance","proficiencyLevel":"Intermediate","inLanguage":"id-ID","isPartOf":{"@type":"WebSite","@id":"https://abyte.id/#website","name":"abyte","url":"https://abyte.id"},"about":{"@type":"Thing","name":"Pengembangan Web"},"speakable":{"@type":"SpeakableSpecification","cssSelector":["h1","article .article-content p"]}}10:T1234,<h2>Apa Itu React Server Components?</h2>

<p>React Server Components (RSC) adalah paradigma baru dalam pengembangan aplikasi React yang memungkinkan komponen dirender langsung di server. Berbeda dengan Server-Side Rendering (SSR) tradisional yang mengirim HTML lengkap ke klien, RSC mengirimkan representasi serial dari komponen tanpa mengikutsertakan JavaScript-nya ke browser.</p>

<p>Dengan kata lain, komponen server tidak menambah ukuran bundle JavaScript di sisi klien. Ini adalah lompatan besar dalam hal performa, terutama untuk aplikasi yang banyak menampilkan konten statis.</p>

<h2>Mengapa RSC Penting?</h2>

<p>Keunggulan utama RSC meliputi:</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>Bundle size lebih kecil</strong> — kode komponen server tidak pernah sampai ke browser</li>
<li><strong>Data fetching langsung</strong> — bisa mengakses database atau API internal tanpa membuat API route terpisah</li>
<li><strong>Keamanan lebih baik</strong> — logika sensitif seperti token dan kredensial tetap di server</li>
<li><strong>Streaming</strong> — konten bisa dikirim secara bertahap sehingga Time to First Byte (TTFB) lebih cepat</li>
</ul>
<h2>Server vs Client Components</h2>

<p>Di Next.js 14, semua komponen secara default adalah <strong>Server Components</strong>. Untuk membuat Client Component, kamu perlu menambahkan direktif <code>'use client'</code> di bagian atas file:</p>

<pre><code class="language-tsx">// app/page.tsx — Server Component (default)
import { db } from '@/lib/db'
import { UserCard } from './UserCard'

<p>export default async function HomePage() {
  const users = await db.user.findMany()</p>

<p>return (
    &lt;main&gt;
      &lt;h1&gt;Daftar Pengguna&lt;/h1&gt;
      {users.map((user) =&gt; (
        &lt;UserCard key={user.id} user={user} /&gt;
      ))}
    &lt;/main&gt;
  )
}
</code></pre></p>

<pre><code class="language-tsx">// app/UserCard.tsx — Client Component
'use client'

<p>import { useState } from 'react'</p>

<p>interface UserCardProps {
  user: { id: string; name: string; email: string }
}</p>

<p>export function UserCard({ user }: UserCardProps) {
  const [expanded, setExpanded] = useState(false)</p>

<p>return (
    &lt;div onClick={() =&gt; setExpanded(!expanded)}&gt;
      &lt;h3&gt;{user.name}&lt;/h3&gt;
      {expanded &amp;&amp; &lt;p&gt;{user.email}&lt;/p&gt;}
    &lt;/div&gt;
  )
}
</code></pre></p>

<h2>Pola Komposisi yang Tepat</h2>

<p>Kunci utama menggunakan RSC adalah <strong>mengarahkan <code>'use client'</code> sedalam mungkin</strong>. Jangan langsung menandai seluruh halaman sebagai client component. Sebagai gantinya, ekstrak hanya bagian interaktif yang membutuhkan state atau event handler.</p>

<pre><code class="language-tsx">// Jangan begini — seluruh halaman jadi client component
'use client'
export default function Dashboard({ data }) {
  const [tab, setTab] = useState('overview')
  // ... seluruh logic di sini
}

<p>// Lakukan begini — pisahkan leaf component interaktif
// DashboardTabs.tsx
'use client'
export function DashboardTabs({ onTabChange }) {
  const [tab, setTab] = useState('overview')
  return &lt;TabBar active={tab} onChange={setTab} onTabChange={onTabChange} /&gt;
}</p>

<p>// page.tsx — tetap server component
export default async function DashboardPage() {
  const data = await fetchDashboardData()
  return &lt;DashboardLayout data={data} /&gt;
}
</code></pre></p>

<h2>Data Fetching di Server Component</h2>

<p>Salah satu keunggulan terbesar RSC adalah kemampuan melakukan data fetching langsung tanpa useEffect atau library client-side:</p>

<pre><code class="language-tsx">import { notFound } from 'next/navigation'

<p>export default async function ArticlePage({
  params,
}: {
  params: { slug: string }
}) {
  const article = await getArticle(params.slug)</p>

<p>if (!article) {
    notFound()
  }</p>

<p>return (
    &lt;article&gt;
      &lt;h1&gt;{article.title}&lt;/h1&gt;
      &lt;time&gt;{article.datePublished}&lt;/time&gt;
      &lt;div dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{ __html: article.content }} /&gt;
    &lt;/article&gt;
  )
}
</code></pre></p>

<h2>Kesimpulan</h2>

<p>React Server Components mengubah cara kita memikirkan arsitektur aplikasi React. Dengan Next.js 14, pola ini sudah menjadi default dan sangat direkomendasikan. Kuncinya adalah: <strong>gunakan server component sebisa mungkin, dan hanya beralih ke client component saat kamu benar-benar membutuhkan interaktivitas di sisi klien</strong>.</p>

<p>Mulai sekarang, biasakan untuk bertanya pada diri sendiri setiap kali membuat komponen baru: "Apakah komponen ini benar-benar perlu jadi client component?" Sebagian besar waktu, jawabannya adalah tidak.</p>2:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$f"}}],["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Beranda\",\"item\":\"https://abyte.id/id\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Artikel\",\"item\":\"https://abyte.id/id/articles\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Menguasai React Server Components di Next.js 14\",\"item\":\"https://abyte.id/id/articles/mastering-server-components-nextjs-14\"}]}"}}],["$","header",null,{"className":"relative bg-gray-900 overflow-hidden","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"absolute inset-0","children":[["$","img",null,{"src":"/uploads/1780240471315-mzhf5c.png","alt":"","className":"w-full h-full object-cover opacity-25 scale-105"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-900/60 via-gray-900/75 to-gray-900"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-8 pb-20 lg:pt-14 lg:pb-28","children":[["$","nav",null,{"aria-label":"Breadcrumb","className":"mb-10","children":["$","ol",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":["$","$Ld",null,{"href":"/id","className":"text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors","children":"Beranda"}]}],["$","li",null,{"aria-hidden":"true","children":["$","svg",null,{"className":"w-3 h-3 text-gray-600","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","strokeWidth":2,"stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","d":"M8.25 4.5l7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5"}]}]}],["$","li",null,{"children":["$","$Ld",null